Two thirds of those surveyed even demand that Deutsche Bank and other lenders exit the business because it exacerbates the problems of the world's poorest.
This is the result of a Forsa survey commissioned by the consumer organization Foodwatch.
The study is based on a report Foodwatch presented in mid-October.
